{"title":"吕家庄优良品种出了名（图片）","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1952,"month":3,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"吕家庄优良品种出了名"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彭彬  任迁乔  彭翰春  作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（四）吕家庄大转变，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家家户户把种籽换。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了庄稼收成好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都到田里把种选。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（五）吕家庄多打了粮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把办法传给外庄上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好种籽换出去一万五千斤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"推广到大小二百五十个庄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（六）勤宣传多推广，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"优良品种走四乡；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年老的、年轻的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁见了好种谁欢喜。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}